{
  "stem": "4513.4",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And to degrade another human being this way, you know, to take away a person's dignity to this extent-- and I think I could relate to that, from the Purdues and all the places I had been, that I just felt that somehow this is awful.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, people shouldn't have to live this way.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Nobody should do another human being this way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That here are people who [? after ?] all those things that everybody thinks people should do to be a decent person and suddenly, through no fault of their own, to be destroyed this way.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that-- how could these men, people, say that they're civilized?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What did-- how did some of these, you know, buddies or some of the others take out their anger?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I had guys firing in the ground.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were doing all sorts of things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They would unload their weapons in the ground.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They-- because we wanted to fight somebody at that point.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And a lot them-- some of the guys just sat staring.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, they was-- but everybody was affected.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was nobody who took this lightly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I saw the-- I saw the furnaces.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was-- they were stacked, like you know, one on top, two or-- two deep, in a long row.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And those I saw.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I didn't see any of those.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we were-- we were just confined to do just what I said there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, we weren't moving any further than we were, because we were under the officers' direction.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And those people came out so we had our hands full just dealing--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--with the crowd, the number of people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And once we knew who they were, just trying to help them as much as we could.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, the living.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
